|WKO___________________________

|YKOPlayers have the option of joining a second guild
once they have attained CHAMPION status at level 50.

Classes describe what a character innately is. They are separate from learned
guild membership and are not choices in the dual-guild system.

There are many restrictions on the available guilds 
that can be chosen as your 'second' guild, including,

|BKB* |CKBYour Race
|BKB* |CKBYour Allegiance to a particular god.
|BKB* |CKBYour existing guilds philosophical beliefs.
|BKB* |CKBThe Exisiting restrictions already in place for
  joining that guild.

|YKOThere might be guilds that remain solo guilds purely
due to the stringent requirements and discipline required
to undertake those role.

You may not join more than 2 guilds. Grimtilla will 
remove either guild for the nominated fee.

You can checkout the guilds you are able to join
via |YKB"help combos"

